schools.name: Veterans Park Academy For The Arts

data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage home is located on an OVERSIZED FULLY FENCED LOT! Entertain with friends and family on the EXTENDED PAVER PATIO. Great room is open to the spacious kitchen with 42" cabinetry, BRAND NEW GE stainless steel appliances, large island & pantry. Primary bedroom features ensuite with dual sinks and large walk in closet. 2 secondary bedrooms with center hall bath. The home has been freshly painted. Town Lakes is a gated community with LOW HOA FEES $275/quarter. Pet Friendly community. Close to shopping and restaurants.
